---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Meet Automancer founder Waseem and the practical approach to AI and workflow automation."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">About</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">
        Hi, I'm Waseem, founder of Automancer. I help small businesses simplify operations
        with practical AI and workflow automation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--light">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Philosophy</span>
      <h2>I believe good automation should:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Remove friction, not create more of it.</li>
        <li>Be easy to understand and maintain.</li>
        <li>Deliver measurable business value.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">How I work</span>
      <h2>Clear, practical, no surprises.</h2>
      <div class="work-cols">
        <div>
          <h3 class="work-col__title">Plain English</h3>
          <p class="work-col__text">No jargon, no buzzwords. I explain what we're doing and why in language everyone on your team can follow.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="work-col__title">Clear scope</h3>
          <p class="work-col__text">Realistic delivery plans with defined boundaries. You'll always know what's included and what to expect.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="work-col__title">Practical handover</h3>
          <p class="work-col__text">Everything is documented and handed over so your team can own and maintain it going forward.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--dark cta-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="cta-block__heading">If your team is stuck in repetitive admin or disconnected workflows, let's talk.</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary"><span>Book a consultation</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
